<template>
  <v-container class="d-flex flex-row justiy-center align-center">
    <v-card :elevation="10" v-for="item in properties" :key="item.property_id">
      <v-card-title> {{ item.property_name }}</v-card-title>
      <v-card-subtitle>{{ item.property_address }}</v-card-subtitle>
    </v-card>
  </v-container>
</template>
<script setup>
import { useStore } from "vuex";
import { onMounted, computed } from "vue";
const store = useStore();
const properites = computed(() => {
  return store.state.property.properties;
});
onMounted(() => {
  store.dispatch("getProperites");
});
</script>
<style scoped></style>
